        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<!-- 04. Donate By: Mahmud Shakir -->
<div id="donate-hp">
    <!-- 04-1. Donate Button Callout -->
    <div id="donate-hp__button">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div id="donate-hp__div">
                <a href="">Help save lives. Donate today.</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- 04-2. Donor Story Preview -->
    <div id="donate-hp__story-preview">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div id="carouselExampleControls story-preview__carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <blockquote class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12">"Temiskaming was fantasic when my gradma got sick. They were kind and helpful. They kept her company when she was scared aswell. It was hard for her since my grandpa passed away last year, but they were amazing. My donation is to thank them for their great work."</blockquote>
                        <p class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12 white">- Jane Smith</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="story-preview__button">
                <a href="">View More Donor Stories</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
